The database query program is in Finnish. It has 5 functions. The database that I have used is from Helsinki University&rsquo;s course &ldquo;Tietokantojen perusteet&rdquo;
How the program works:
 Calculate the total number of course credits earned in a given year Print all the transcript of study records of a given student in chronological order Print the distribution of study record grades for a given course Print the top x teachers who has given the most credits Close the program  You can see example how the database query program works here
